<taxonomicName id="E6659DB6F290792EB50EC013666B6BC5" class="Pucciniomycetes" genus="Uredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Uredo mbelensis" order="Pucciniales" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="mbelensis">Uredo mbelensis</taxonomicName>
in her monograph. With the new ICN, this species can now be recognized in the appropriate genus.
</paragraph>
